quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Ruri! Qura’n Re e senotse ka bosiu ba matla
  97,2,Ke eng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na bosiu ba matla ke eng
  97,3,Bosiu ba matla bo molemo ho feta likhoeli tse sekete
  97,4,Ke nako eo manyeloi le Khabariele ba theohelang lefats’eng ka tumello ea Mong`a bona le ka melao eohle
  97,5,Khotso!... Sena Ho fihlela chabo ea letsatsi